(fifthQuint)PET Imaging of Intracranial Cancers With 18F-FSPG.

 Subjects with various types and grades of primary brain tumors or brain metastasis will be recruited.

 The brain tumor needs to be either histologically or clinically confirmed.

 18F-FSPG will be injected intravenously into the subjects, and PET/CT imaging performed.

 Images will be assessed visually and quantitatively.

 Available tumor specimens will be analyzed by immunohistochemistry (IHC) for example for expression of components of the system xc- and associated biomarkers.

